(1, 'index', 'index', '2', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Welcome to the Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center</h4>\r\n<h1> Our Mission</h1>\r\n<h4><i>"A tradition of caring since 1982"</i></h4>\r\n<br>\r\n</div>', '<p>The facility is committed to being the leading provider of quality long term care, short term rehab, personal care, independent living, and related health care services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center is dedicated to meeting the clinical, functional, psychosocial and emotional needs of the residents. By challenging our care givers to provide innovative health care services and pursuing more effective ways of treating the residents, we believe the residents, through personal initiative and encouragement by others, can attain the highest quality of life possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The residents and their families will receive quality service in a caring and compassionate atmosphere that recognizes each individual&#39;s needs and rights.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(2, '', '', '7', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Quiet Community Setting </h4>\r\n<h1>Exceptional Quality of Care </h1>\r\n<h4>all provided in Forest City </h4>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<p>Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center is a 132 bed facility nestled in the country setting of a small community. We have served the needs of our residents since 1982. Residents and their families are invited to participate in the many activities offered on a daily basis. You can take advantage of the spacious family room, comfortable sitting room,  outdoor pavilion and Meditation Garden while enjoying the picturesque scenery that changes with the four seasons</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our goal is to bring individuals to their highest level of functioning while protecting and promoting their rights. Our caring staff and home-like environment provide a warm, compassionate atmosphere for our long-term and short term residents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Residents are encouraged to bring cherished possessions in order to preserve their association with family and friends. We recommend that residents and families participate in decision making through attendance at their individualized care plan meetings.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<div class="contentTileImgContainer">\r\n<img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/care.jpg">\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(4, '', 'personalcare', '4', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>We Can Meet All Your Needs With</h4>\r\n<h1> Different Levels of Care </h1>\r\n<h4>Offered at Forest City Personal Care</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p><b>Respite Care</b><br>\r\nCaring for a loved one at home can be challenging at times.  There are periods where you need to rest and recharge as a family caregiver.  Let us help you with that.  Respite services allow us to care for your loved one while you get your well deserved TLC.  \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Independent Living</b><br>\r\nTake a proactive approach to ensuring a long quality of life.  We offer cost effective independent living suites to those who are looking for a safe and secure residence with many desirable amenities.  If you are self sufficient and require little assistance from others, this is the perfect option for you!  \r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(6, 'index', 'index', '5', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Quality Care Begins With the Staff</h4>\r\n<h1>A Dedicated Team of Caregivers </h1>\r\n<h4>Ensure Your Loved One Receives the Best Care Possible</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<div class="textBlockContainer">\r\n<p>Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center promotes job satisfaction for our staff. Numerous members of our team have served our resident&#39;s needs for over twenty years.</p>\r\n<p>Take some time to meet our dedicated staff who contribute the necessary ingredients to enhance the physical, mental, and psychosocial needs of our residents. Our highly regarded reputation is a direct outcome of the level of commitment provided by our staff. </p>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n  <a class="btn btn-maroon" href="contact/staff">Meet Our Team <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span> </a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n  \r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(7, 'information', 'departments', '3', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>An enjoyable recovery begins with an</h4>\r\n<h1>Active Rehabilitation </h1>\r\n<h4>in conjunction with social stimulation</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n</div>', '<div class="tileText">\r\n<p>\r\nWhen you experience the enjoyment that our activities department brings to our residents you&#39;ll understand why this department is so important to our facility.  A continually evolving program makes for an entertaining and here at Forest City Nursing & Rehab. Smiles are definitely contagious among the activities staff and they are guaranteed to brighten your day. </p>\r\n<p>The Activities Department is supervised by a certified activities director and programs are designed to elicit the resident&#39;s physical, mental and social needs.  Stimulation is provided in small and large groups, as well as one on one.  \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<!-- <a href="#" class="btn btn-maroon">Become a Volunteer <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span> </a> -->\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(8, 'information', 'departments', '2', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Delicious Cuisine Leads to a Great</h4>\r\n<h1>Dining Experience</h1>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>As you pass by our Dietary department around meal times you can typically catch an alluring aroma of wonderfully cooked cuisine.  Our on-site registered dietician makes every effort to make each individual&#39;s dining experience enjoyable.  Input is gathered monthly to adjust menu choices to better match the preferences of our residents. Well balanced meals are prepared in-house daily and regular and therapeutic diets can be provided, based on the recommendations of your physician.  To retain your interest, we have developed a five week rotating menu that changes with the seasons.      \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nSpacious dining halls are open to anyone who wishes to share a meal with their loved one. \r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(9, 'information', 'departments', '7', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>A clean home like environment is made possible with </h4>\r\n<h1>Our friendly housekeeping staff</h1>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p> Our Environmental Services team takes great pride in providing you with exceptionally clean and odor free surroundings.  We recognize that while you are staying with us, this is your home, and we will treat it as such.  Daily housekeeping and laundry services let you relax as you continue your recovery process. Cleanliness is also very important when preventing the spread of disease and infection.   We encourage you to walk through our facility, and see firsthand, the our standard of cleanliness.\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(10, 'information', 'departments', '4', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Preparedness and Prevention Results in</h4>\r\n<h1>Uninterrupted Services</h1>\r\n<h4>Thanks to Our Maintenance Staff</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>We have strategically designed a disaster preparedness program to ensure that our residents will always receive uninterrupted services regardless of external circumstances.  This level of safety and security may not always be available for individuals receiving care in their homes.  Families find comfort in knowing their loved ones are in a dependable environment. Our fire alert and protection systems are an additional layer of security that are provided to our residents that is difficult to recreate in a residential home setting. </p>\r\n<p>\r\nThe wandering resident is kept safe by our Code Alert System, which notifies staff of a potential elopement risk. Individuals are able to be redirected before they face risk.\r\n </p>\r\n<p>\r\nThe maintenance staff takes pride in their preventative maintenance program. Prevention is a key factor in the preservation and function of the many types of equipment used by our residents which sustains quality of life.  Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center also appreciates the outstanding job done by the Maintenance Department in keeping the grounds pristine for residents and visitors to enjoy.\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(11, 'information', 'departments', '5', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Rain, Sleet, Snow, or Shine,</h4>\r\n<h1>Our Medical & Nursing Staff</h1>\r\n<h4>provide the best quality of care to our residents</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p> \r\n\r\nThere is no doubt the job of a nurse is no easy task.  Our highly skilled team of Licensed Nurses and Certified Nursing Assistants has provided care to our community since 1982. Our nursing department receives regular education and is up to date with the current medical procedures, treatments, and standards.  We are here to meet all of your needs, not just solely those related to your medical health.  Our facility provides numerous medical and ancillary services that are guaranteed to make your stay with us comfortable and enjoyable.          \r\n\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(12, 'information', 'departments', '6', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Effective rehabilitation is made possible by our</h4>\r\n<h1>Therapy Team</h1>\r\n<h4>a dedicated staff of professionals</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n   <!-- <img class=" img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/pt.jpg" /> -->\r\n     <!--   <img class="center-block img-circle" src="/resources/images/dept/therapy.jpg" />  -->\r\n</div>', '<div class="textBlockContainer">\r\n\r\n<p> The main focus of the therapy department here at the Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center is to develop and maintain the maximum quality of life for our residents. Our comprehensive rehab program includes physical, speech, and occupational therapies delivered by qualified therapists in our state-of-the art rehab clinic. The rehab staff collaborates extensively with other departments to analyze the needs of each individual to ensure a rapid recovery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> We provide a safe environment for individuals who may have undergone surgery or a recent hospital stay in which they can revive the services needed to help get them back on their feet.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Personalized Therapy Services Include:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li> <p> Rehabilitation for Joint Replacement, Fractures, etc. </p></li>\r\n        <li> <p>Stroke Rehabilitation</p></li>\r\n	<li> <p>Activities of Daily Living </p></li>\r\n	<li> <p>Electronic Stimulation</p></li>\r\n	<li> <p>Home Safety Assessments </p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(13, 'information', 'departments', '1', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Need Assistance adjusting to continuing care?</h4>\r\n<h1>Our Qualified Social Workers</h1>\r\n<h4>are here to help make adjusting effortless</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n', '<p>\r\nSocial Services acts as the narrator as you begin your journey through this continuum of care.  Whether you&#39;re only staying a short time for rehabilitation or you plan to call Forest City Nursing & Rehab your final residence, Social Services is here to ensure a pleasant stay.  Our Social Services Department understands that seeking quality care can be hectic and overwhelming.  They are here to relieve you of the burdens associated with this new transition. In choosing to stay at Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center, you will find comfort and assurance knowing that your expectations will be satisfied.  \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> <strong>As much as we hate to see you go, we are happy to see you leave. </strong> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Typically, most people hate to say goodbye, however, most often at Forest City Nursing & Rehab this is exciting time.  Many of our residents, through our rehabilitation program, have met their rehab goals and are able to transition from our home to their&#39;s.  Others are able to function in a lower level of care where they are able to exercise more independence.  Social Services is instrumental in coordinating the resident&#39;s discharge from the facility. They review the resident&#39;s future needs and preferences, make referrals to various agencies as applicable, and obtains supportive services to ensure for a safe discharge.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThe Social Services Department is staffed by licensed Social Workers who are happy to answer any questions or provide a tour of the facility upon request. Please contact Mary Ann or Laura at 570-785-3005.\r\n</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(23, 'services', 'independent', '1', '1', '<img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/independent.jpg"/>', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4> </h4>\r\n<h1> Independent Living </h1>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p> Independent Living at Forest City Personal Care is your first step in a journey to peace of mind and security as you retire in a comfortable, safe living community. The facility, located in the town of Forest City, is nestled in the picturesque hills and valleys of Northeast PA. We are a one floor community, easily accessible with the safety and convenience of our residents in mind. \r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'grayPattern', 'grayPattern'),
(14, 'information', 'admissions', '1', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h1>Admissions Information</h1>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>Our professional and compassionate social service staff have numerous years of experience and expertise at Forest City Nursing and Rehab Center. They are skillful in orientating new residents and staff to our facility.  During the admission process, the social worker will answer all your questions related to living accommodations, payment sources, medical care, therapy services, discharge planning, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Families are invited to attend their loved one&#39;s Care Plan meets to discuss their progress and any concerns that they may have about their loved one&#39;s care and future goals.</p>\r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(15, 'information', 'employment', '1', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Are you a kind and caring person?</h4>\r\n<h1>Join Our Team</h1>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>Forest City Nursing and Rehab Center is a 132 bed facility employing caregivers from Forest City and neighboring communities. Our philosophy is to respect the individual rights of each employee and to treat all employees with courtesy, dignity, and consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a fantastic staff here at the Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center and we maintain this characteristic by hiring individuals who demonstrate an attitude that will positively impact our organization. We seek persons who are highly motivated and have the passion and drive to succeed. If this describes you, chances are you will be a great fit for our organization. Please fill out an application for a open position listed below.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(16, 'contact', 'staff', '1', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h1> Meet Our Team </h1>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>Take some time to get to know some of the wonderful staff members here at the Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center. These are only a few of the individuals who serve our residents on a daily basis.  There is a long list of over 100 team members who contribute to meeting our organization&#39;s goals and ensure continuous ongoing success. We are all committed to provide you and your loved one with the highest level of respect and quality to services. Please feel free to contact anyone of our team members with inquiries you may have. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(18, '', 'personalcare', '1', '1', '<img class="center-block img-circle" src="/resources/images/PersonalCare.png"/>', '<h1>Personal Care</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Forest City Personal Care is a fully licensed facility committed to the care of the elderly who need limited assistance in order to maintain their independence.  Supervised care is provided by trained, qualified staff under the direction of the Administrator, Marcy Kerzic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We invite you to enjoy the scenic Four Seasons of Pennsylvania at our spacious personal care residence designed with you in mind.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'grayPattern', 'grayPattern'),
(19, '', '', '5', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Enjoy Stimulating</h4>\r\n<h1> Daily Activities </h1>\r\n<h4>That Promote Social Interaction</h4>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>The residents are provided a monthly calendar of all events.  Activities include exercise programs, games, musical entertainment, religious services, event parties, outdoor activities, as well as arts and crafts.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(20, '', 'personalcare', '2', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Sometimes it&#39;s the simple things that</h4>\r\n<h1> Give Peace of Mind </h1>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p> At our personal care home, we make life easier by providing single floor living accommodations. We offer you the option of either private or semi-private suites and invite you to personalize it to your liking. Staff will assist as needed with: medication management, coordination of healthcare services, and bathing and dressing. Comfortable dining amenities are provided for a restaurant style dining experience. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Residents find rest and relaxation as they leave behind the daily stresses associated with living alone. Our facility provides you with daily housekeeping and laundry services. Therapy services can be provided on-site, on an as needed basis. </p>\r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(22, 'services', 'respiteCare', '1', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4> </h4>\r\n<h1>  </h1>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n\r\n<img class="img-thumbnail center-block" src="/resources/images/respitePhoto.jpg"/>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h1> Respite Care </h1>\r\n<h4>Rest, Re-Group, and Recharge</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="textBlockContainer">\r\n\r\n<p> \r\nRespite Care Services are designed to provide relief for the caregiver or family member by allowing them to step away from their day-to-day responsibilities.\r\nEach year, many people make the conscious decision to provide crucial living assistance for their spouses, family members, or friends. Over a period of time, caring for those stricken by disabilities can take a physical and emotional toll on the caregiver. Respite Care provides the means to make provisions for a temporary stay with us, allowing the caregiver some time for rest and relaxation. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nFor more information please contact us, one of our social workers will be happy to provide you more information and address any of your questions concerning our respite services. \r\n</p>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<a href="/contact/sendMessage" class="btn btn-maroon">Contact Us <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(24, 'services', 'independent', '2', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4>Being Proactive with Your Future Ensures</h4>\r\n<h1>A Stress Free Retirement</h1>\r\n<h4>What is it All About?</h4>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>Looking beyond retirement is not usually something most people do until a life event warrants change. However there are many benefits to planning post retirement before arrangements are necessary. Here at the Forest City Personal Care, we offer a cost efficient option.  Our Independent Living service allows you to leave the worries and stresses associated with residential living behind.</p>\r\n<p>Often times, individuals relocate their residence multiple times in order to meet their changing lifestyle needs.  Choosing to start your post retirement in one of our independent living suits will ensure minimal disruption as your health care needs change; we offer three levels of care, all on one campus!  It is never too soon or too late to start!  We ensure you the satisfaction of knowing that your well-being will be looked after as you progress through life.  Call and schedule a tour with our Administrator and see if you meet the necessary qualifications.\r\n</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(25, 'services', 'independent', '3', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h1>Suite Amenities</h1>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>Indoor amenities include two large comfortable carpeted living rooms, one with a built-in fire place and mantle.  Private and semi-private suites are available and living arrangements for spouses can be made available upon request.  Our suites are furnished with comfortable beds, chairs, dressers and lamps; however, we invite our clients to bring items that will complement their personal likes and reflect the decor that portrays their individual taste.   Restaurant style dining is available for all meals in our spacious dining room.  We have a private parking lot for those individuals who wish to have their vehicle on campus.  Additionally, we also provide cable access and free Wi-Fi.  Outdoor amenities include beautifully decorated twin porches conveniently accessible from the dining room and living room. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(26, 'contact', 'staff', '2', '4', '<div class=" employeeImgContainer">\r\n         <img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/drewS.jpg"/> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=""></div>', '<div class="employeeDescription center-block">\r\n\r\n<h4>Administrator, Owner</h4>\r\n<h1>Drew Sparks </h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Drew Sparks, LNHA, facility administrator and owner has been involved with our facility since 1984. Through the years, it&#39;s been Drew&#39;s philosophy that the resident&#39;s needs always come first. His main priority is that residents and families are pleased with the exceptional care and services delivered by Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center and Forest City Personal Care. Drew resides in Clifford Township with his wife and two sons. He enjoys spending time with his family, being outdoors, golfing and riding his motorcycle.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(27, 'contact', 'staff', '3', '4', '<div class=" employeeImgContainer">\r\n	<img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/lisaD.jpg"/>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=""></div>', '<div class="employeeDescription center-block">\r\n\r\n<h4>Assistant Administrator of Resident Services</h4>\r\n<h1>Lisa Demchak </h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Lisa Demchak, RN, NHA has served the residents of Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center for the past 30 years. She started her career as a nursing assistant, obtained her nursing degree from Penn State University, and is currently employed as the Assistant Administrator of Resident Services. Lisa does not manage behind her desk but takes an active hands-on approach to ensure the highest quality of care is delivered to our residents. In her spare time Lisa enjoys traveling and time with family, especially her two children. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(28, 'contact', 'staff', '4', '4', '<div class=" employeeImgContainer">\r\n	<img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/sueL.jpg"/>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=""></div>', '<div class="employeeDescription center-block">\r\n\r\n<h4>Director of Nursing</h4>\r\n<h1>Susan Loomis </h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Susan Loomis, Director of Nursing has more than 15 years as a Director of Nursing as well as experience in multiple other long term care positions. She is proud to be able to say she began her long term care career here in 1984 as a nursing assistant. Her knowledge and expertise make her one of the most valuable and respected members of our team. She is the first one to lend a helping hand or offer a solution to a problem.\r\nSue and her family reside at Lake Wallenpaupack. When not working, she enjoys teaching Sunday School, taking beach vacations, and most of all spending time with her daughters and grandchildren. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(29, 'contact', 'staff', '5', '4', '<div class=" employeeImgContainer">\r\n	<img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/maryR.jpg"/>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=""></div>', '<div class="employeeDescription center-block">\r\n\r\n<h4>Director of Social Services</h4>\r\n<h1>Mary Ann Rogan</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Mary Ann is a graduate of Marywood University with both a Bachelors and Masters Degree in Social Work. She began her career working in Mental Health before taking a position in the hospital setting. She transitioned to the Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center in 1993 as the director of Social Services. Throughout her experiences at the facility, she has had the pleasure of meeting and assisting many residents and families as they continue their journey through life. She is married with two children and enjoys spending time with her family, taking long walks, as well as cooking and baking.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(30, 'contact', 'staff', '6', '4', '<div class=" employeeImgContainer">\r\n	<img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/lisaO.jpg"/>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=""></div>', '<div class="employeeDescription center-block">\r\n\r\n<h4> Dietitian </h4>\r\n<h1>Lisa Ocenas</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Lisa Ocenas holds a Bachelor of Science degree from Marywood University and is our on-site dietitian. She has worked in several clinical settings since May, 1980. As a Registered Dietitian she has enjoyed many experiences at the Forest City Nursing and Rehab Center over the last 25 years. When she visits the residents to determine their food preferences and formulate their nutritional care plan, she also learns so many of their amazing life experiences which she finds very interesting. She is married to her husband John for over 34 years. Together they have two children John Matthew and Kristen who are enjoying their careers in the business world. She is grateful for her professional journey at the Forest City Nursing and Rehab Center and appreciates caring for for the residents and their nutritional needs.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(31, 'contact', 'staff', '7', '4', '<div class="employeeImgContainer">\r\n	<img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/jenP2.jpg"/>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=""></div>', '<div class="employeeDescription center-block">\r\n\r\n<h4>Activities Director </h4>\r\n<h1>Jennifer Portz</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><i>" After graduating from Delaware Valley High School in Milford PA I moved to South Florida and became a licensed SCUBA Instructor. For almost ten years I taught and certified over one thousand people from the ages of 12 to 65 and safely logged over 5,000 dives. But my students taught me something as well. I learned the value and meaning of Quality of Life. In 2005 I moved back to PA and  dedicated myself to serving our older adult community as a resident aide in a personal care home. It was there I learned something else, that people, no matter what theyâ€™re age, gender or race still have the desire to learn new things and have quality and meaning in their daily life. In 2011 I received my C.N.A. certification through Marywood University and began working in Skilled Nursing Centers. While working as a C.N.A. it became clear to me that our senior population was being wonderfully cared for medically by the nurses and aides, but mental, physical, spiritual, social and emotional needs were the responsibility of the activities department. In 2015 I became a certified Activity Director with a mission to bring meaningful quality activities to our older adult population; finding purpose, dignity  and pride in what they can still learn to do and accomplish."</i></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(32, 'contact', 'staff', '8', '4', '<div class=" employeeImgContainer">\r\n	 <img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/markV3.jpg"/> \r\n           <!--    <img class="img-circle center-block" src="/resources/images/dept/markV2.jpg"/> -->\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=""></div>', '<div class="employeeDescription center-block">\r\n\r\n<h4>Director of Maintenance </h4>\r\n<h1>Mark VonAhnen</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class="text-muted">Mark has over ten years experience as a maintenance supervisor in Long Term Care and we have had the pleasure of his knowledge and expertise at Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center since 2010.  He is licensed as a home builder and general contractor and still enjoys repairing and remodeling homes in his spare time.  Markâ€™s friendly attitude and positive outlook makes him a great leader who is not afraid to roll up his sleeves and take on any problem.  He has a huge impact on the lives of all our residents, staff, and visitors and enjoys seeing firsthand the satisfaction that facility enhancements bring to them.  In his spare time, Mark enjoys spending time with his wife, who also works at Forest City Nursing & Rehab Center as a Nurse Supervisor, and their two dogs.  Additionally, he enjoys a relaxing night out including dinner and movies with family and friends.  Mark especially enjoys the rare opportunity to take a road trip with his wife in their 1971 Volkswagen Karman-Ghia convertible.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
(54, 'personalcare', 'admissions', '1', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h1>Admissions Information</h1>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>\r\nLet Forest City Personal Care ease your mind knowing that your loved one is well taken care of in a safe and secure environment. There comes a time where living on your own can become challenging.  Daily activities are now not as effortless as they once were.  Let us provide that additional assistance you may need in order to continue living that independent lifestyle.  Whether you struggle with bathing, dressing, medication management, or could just possibly use some increased social interaction, we aim to meet all of your needs so you can maintain the highest possible level of physical, mental, and social well-being.  Call and schedule a tour with our Administrator and learn more about what we can offer you!       \r\n\r\n</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
(33, 'index', 'index', '3', '5', '<div class="col-sm-3">\r\n	<div class="thumbnail">\r\n      <img src="/resources/images/longTerm.jpg" class="img-circle">\r\n      <div class="caption">\r\n        <h3 >Skilled Nursing</h3>\r\n        <p>Our 132 bed nursing facility promotes peace of mind by providing 24 hour nursing care in a warm compassionate home-like environment.</p>\r\n        <p><a href="/services/skilledNursing" class="center-block btn btn-maroon" role="button">Learn More <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a> </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-sm-3">\r\n	<div class="thumbnail">\r\n      <img src="/resources/images//therapy4.jpg" class="img-circle">\r\n      <div class="caption">\r\n        <h3>Rehab<span class="hidden-sm">ilitation</span></h3>\r\n        <p>Our rehab team promotes rapid recovery for those who need therapy services to return to their former level of independence.  </p>\r\n        <p><a href="/services/rehabilitation" class="center-block btn btn-maroon" role="button">Learn More <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a> </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-sm-3">\r\n	<div class="thumbnail">\r\n      <!--<img src="/resources/images/hospice.png" class="img-circle"> -->\r\n            <img src="/resources/images/newImages/preview.jpg" class="img-circle">\r\n      <div class="caption">\r\n        <h3>Hospice</h3>\r\n        <p>We provide the desired level of comfort for those who require spiritual, emotional and physical support during their final days.</p>\r\n        <p><a href="/services/hospice" class="center-block btn btn-maroon" role="button">Learn More <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a> </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="col-sm-3">\r\n	<div class="thumbnail">\r\n      <img src="/resources/images/personalCareCircle.jpg" class="img-circle">\r\n      <div class="caption">\r\n        <h3>Personal Care</h3>\r\n        <p>Forest City Personal Care provides care and services to individuals who need limited assistance to maintain their desired lifestyle. </p>\r\n        <p><a href="/personalcare" class="center-block btn btn-maroon" role="button">Learn More <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a> </p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'thumbnailNav', 'contentTile thumbnailNav'),
(38, '', '', '2', '1', '<div class="tileHeadingText">\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h1>Certified Nursing Assistant</h1>\r\n<h4>7:00am - 3:00pm</h4>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><b>Position Description</b><br>\r\nHere is a description for the job position.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Desired Skills</b><br>\r\nThese are some of the desired skills for this position</p>\r\n\r\n<h6>Posted on 12/28/2015</h6>\r\n<a class="btn btn-maroon" target="_blank" href="/EmploymentApplication.pdf" download>Apply Now <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></a>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL),
